data.description: Look no further if you need a newer ranch style home. This 4 bed and 2 bath home has amazing hardwood floors, and a great open floor plan with a beautiful kitchen. The master bedroom offers a great bathroom and walk-in closet. The 4th bedroom gives a great option for a home office. The back yard is a great size for the kids, dogs, or nice fire on a fall evening. With no HOA you can enjoy your property without a long list of rules and restrictions. Please schedule your showing today, because this one isn't going to last long!
